               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400817-name-894" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18400817-name-894" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400817-name-894" type="surname" value="SMITH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400817-name-894" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS SMITH</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Samuel-row, West Hackney, and am a carter. On the 17th of July I stopped at a public-house on Cambridge-heath—I left my cart at the door with my shovel in it—I saw it taken out by the prisoner—I ran out, and my mate laid hold of him, when he got about twenty yards from the cart—he asked him what he was going to do—he said, "To pawn it for half a gallon of beer."</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400817-name-895" type="witnessName">
